HEADWORD: hard-bound
<hw>hard"-bound`</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Having rigid front and
back covers, usually boards covered with paper, cloth, or leather; -- of
books. Contrasted with <contr>softcover</contr> and
<contr>paperback</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

